                Below is a map I created to help me keep track of most of the places I have been. Mostly
                the cities or interesting sites rather than every random little place.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="content" >
            <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1q3bVL-stJndcmIi1kl-DEBTNDtm7gRc&ehbc=2E312F&noprof=1" width="1280" height="640"></iframe>
        </div>
    </article>
